==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Recension
<hw>Re*cen"sion</hw> <pr>(r⟦esl⟧*s⟦ecr⟧n"sh⟦ucr⟧n)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos>
<ety>[L. <ets>recensio</ets>: cf. F. <ets>recension</ets>.]</ety>
<sn>1.</sn> <def>The act of reviewing or revising; review; examination;
enumeration.</def> <rj><au>Barrow.</au></rj>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><sn>2.</sn> <def>Specifically, the review of a text (as of an ancient
author) by an editor; critical revisal and establishment.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><sn>3.</sn> <def>The result of such a work; a text established by
critical revision; an edited version.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Recensionist</ent>⟦br⟧
